\pard\f0\fs28  Subgen.{\b  Graminifolii} Buchenau. Perennials with a rhizome. Leaves several, basal and cauline, flat or involute to rarely canaliculate, without marginal sclerenchyma-strands. Inflorescence terminal; involucral bracteoles absent. Seeds with or without appendages.
