\pard\f0\fs28  Subgen.{\b  Ensifolii} (Snogerup) Snogerup. Perennials; rhizome well-developed. All leaves on flowering stems. Leaves ensiform pluritubulose, imperfectly septate throughout. Flowers in heads; involucral bracteoles absent. Stamens shorter than perianth-segments. Seeds without appendages.
\par

